{"id":4963,"title":"[New fall prediction score for the prevention of fall fractures in the elderly].","abstract":"Elderly fracture is a critical public health issue for older adults, and falls risk assessment is an expected competency for medical worker. The prevention from fall fracture is one of the important items of medical safety, and although fall assessment is carried out, it is not much effective. One of the reasons is that there is not the simple and easy tool of the fall prediction. The aim of this study was to design an innovative method of falls risk assessment using standing ability of the elderly. We devised new fall assessment score (Mimamori score) that scored lifting assistance movement. We incorporate it in real duties after 2011, inflect for the fall prevention.","date":"2014-12-15","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25509807","annotations":[{"name":"Health","weight":0.812486,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Public health","weight":0.801318,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Public_health"},{"name":"Safety","weight":0.752457,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Safety"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.732949,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.675125,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.526731,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"Tool","weight":0.396419,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tool"},{"name":"Design","weight":0.391104,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Design"},{"name":"Old age","weight":0.27754,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_age"},{"name":"Skill","weight":0.213361,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skill"},{"name":"Risk assessment","weight":0.211144,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk_assessment"},{"name":"Workforce","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Workforce"},{"name":"Evaluation","weight":0.038706,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evaluation"},{"name":"Public","weight":0.0311179,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Public"},{"name":"Prediction","weight":0.0227187,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prediction"},{"name":"2011","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2011"},{"name":"Film score","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Film_score"},{"name":"Inflection","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inflection"},{"name":"Real number","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Real_number"},{"name":"Corporation","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corporation"},{"name":"Social movement","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_movement"},{"name":"Fracture","weight":0.0111494,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fracture"}]}
